lead_paragraph: Megan Podkowa scored a career-high 29 points, hitting 12 of her 15 shots, to help No. 25 DePaul hold off St. John's 71-61 on Sunday night.

headline.print_headline: Podkowa Scores 29 to Lead No. 25 DePaul Women by St. John's
